Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.61,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人憂傷的純粹簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.95,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕陽西下時的道場一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}揮灑著汗水練習刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.59,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人發笑的滿腔熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.89,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有夢想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.79,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般這樣大聲叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:49.10,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝陽東昇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:52.07,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你會在喧鬧的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.12,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拚命奔跑著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.18,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:01.03,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降臨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:04.09,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你會穿過寬闊的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.13,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河灘邊訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.00,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是這樣吧 我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.60,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.26,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一顆赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.49,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守護著重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:25.49,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}臉上透露著決心吧
